<section><div class="section-inner"><div class="grid-2"><div><h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2><p style="color:var(--c6);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.25rem">Efficient Resources Trading Sdn. Bhd. (Reg. 1162913-D) is a Malaysian-based industrial rubber recycling and trading company headquartered in Kamunting Industrial Estate, Perak. We specialize in the collection, processing, and responsible export of unvulcanized rubber scrap (Basel Code B3040).</p><p style="color:var(--c6);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.25rem">Our operations are built on the principles of Environmentally Sound Management (ESM) as defined by the Basel Convention, ensuring every kilogram of rubber scrap is processed, tracked, and shipped to the highest international standards.</p><p style="color:var(--c6);line-height:1.8">We are fully prepared for the EU's new Waste Shipment Regulation (2024/1157), including mandatory DIWASS digital filing and the 2027 facility audit requirements.</p></div><div><div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--g7),var(--g9));border-radius:16px;padding:2.5rem;color:var(--wh);text-align:center"><div style="font-size:3.5rem;margin-bottom:.75rem">&#9851;</div><h3 style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:.75rem;font-family:'DM Sans'">Zero Waste Policy</h3><p style="font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.7">Every piece of unvulcanized rubber scrap is given a second life. Nothing goes to landfill.</p></div></div></div></div></section>
<section class="bg-light"><div class="section-inner"><div class="section-label">Certifications</div><h2 class="section-title">Fully Licensed &amp; Certified</h2><div class="grid-4" style="margin-top:2rem"><div class="card"><h3>SIRIM Certified</h3><p>Valid SIRIM Certificate of Approval for rubber scrap processing.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>MITI Licensed</h3><p>Full MITI export/import permits for international waste trade.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>DOE Compliant</h3><p>Department of Environment compliance for scheduled waste handling.</p></div><div class="card placeholder"><h3>ISO Certification</h3><p>Please provide ISO certification details if applicable.</p></div></div></div></section>
